&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;4-6 SESSION GP PARTNER OR SALARIED GP - CRANESWATER GROUP PRACTICE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;SOUTHSEA, PORTSMOUTH, HAMPSHIRE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are looking for a GP Partner/Salaried GP to work alongside our dynamic &amp; friendly team, in this high achieving practice only a stone’s throw away from the seafront&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Benefits include&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A dedicated team of 5 GP partners, 2 salaried doctors, a nurse practitioner plus 3 practice nurse and 3 HCAs&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Established training practice with the successful applicant having the opportunity to develop this role&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Flexibility in hours, sessions and special interests welcome&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Good CQC rating and High QOF achievement and consistently one of the highest rated practice overall for patient experience in National GP Patient Survey&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Portsmouth TARGET - 10 protected education/ practice development sessions each year&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Member of Portsmouth South Coast Network , with shared Pharmacist and Social Prescriber&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Member of Portsmouth Primary Care Alliance who deliver extended access and acute visiting services to support local practices&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Prior to ‘lockdown’ we were offering:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;15 minute routine booked appointments&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Walk-in surgery and duty team for management of on the day demand&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Appointments from 2 established sites in Southsea&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;A partner would start at parity; for a salaried GP we offer an attractive financial package including payment of medical defence fees&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Informal enquiries and visits welcome.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
